21:17.401 --> 21:20.988
wanna be on the team.

21:22.281 --> 21:23.866
Nick, you've made

21:22.281 --> 21:23.866
a commitment.

21:23.908 --> 21:25.743
Yeah, but still...

21:25.785 --> 21:27.453
And you're very

21:25.785 --> 21:27.453
good at it.

21:27.494 --> 21:28.788
But I don't like it.

21:30.581 --> 21:32.917
Oh, look, it's only until

21:30.581 --> 21:32.917
the end of the year.

21:32.959 --> 21:34.293
Next year,

21:32.959 --> 21:34.293
you'll be at Poulter,

21:34.334 --> 21:35.502
and if you don't wanna

21:34.334 --> 21:35.502
play basketball,

21:35.544 --> 21:37.171
then, sweetheart,

21:35.544 --> 21:37.171
you don't have to.

