Poulter has

21:39.048 --> 21:41.300
an excellent squash team.

21:39.048 --> 21:41.300
They're nationally ranked.

21:42.760 --> 21:43.803
You like squash.

21:48.933 --> 21:50.768
-Hey, there.

21:48.933 --> 21:50.768
-Oh, hey, Sam.

21:50.810 --> 21:52.311
This is Grace's.

21:52.352 --> 21:55.940
Oh, she'd be heartbroken

21:52.352 --> 21:55.940
if she lost this.

21:55.982 --> 21:58.818
She gave it to her father

21:55.982 --> 21:58.818
when she was a little girl.

21:58.859 --> 22:01.862
I think I know why she doesn't

21:58.859 --> 22:01.862
wanna take her driving test.

22:01.904 --> 22:03.030
She misses her dad so much.

22:03.614 --> 22:05.365
Yeah, I'm sorry.

22:05.407 --> 22:07.701
Hard enough losing Jake,

22:05.407 --> 22:07.701
but watching Grace

22:07.743 --> 22:10.163
and Lori and Brandon

22:07.743 --> 22:10.163
lose their father...

22:10.204 --> 22:11.872
I've never known

22:10.204 --> 22:11.872
loss like that.

22:11.914 --> 22:13.332
I hope you never do.

22:13.373 --> 22:16.085
And like everything you do,

22:13.373 --> 22:16.085
you make it look effortless.

22:17.377 --> 22:20.089
You can talk to me

22:17.377 --> 22:20.089
about this, anytime.

22:20.923 --> 22:23.176
I'm a pretty good listener.

22:23.217 --> 22:26.344
Grace would be really upset

22:23.217 --> 22:26.344
if she knew we were

22:23.217 --> 22:26.344
having this conversation.

22:26.386 --> 22:27.345
What conversation?

22:29.723 --> 22:32.101
There's nothing worse than

22:29.723 --> 22:32.101
seeing your child in pain,

22:32.143 --> 22:34.352
knowing no matter what you do,

22:32.143 --> 22:34.352
you can't fix it for them.

22:45.198 --> 22:46.364
(EXHALING)

22:48.159 --> 22:49.702
-(KNOCKING ON DOOR)

