-Come in.

22:49.743 --> 22:51.912
-Hey.

22:49.743 --> 22:51.912
-Michael!

22:53.873 --> 22:55.249
Come, come, sit.

22:58.836 --> 23:02.173
Michael, there is

22:58.836 --> 23:02.173
a slight problem

22:58.836 --> 23:02.173
with your father.

23:03.841 --> 23:05.218
Is this about

23:03.841 --> 23:05.218
my cell phone bill?

23:05.259 --> 23:07.928
No... Wait, what bill?

23:07.970 --> 23:09.471
(SIGHS) Never mind.

23:09.513 --> 23:12.766
No, your father is insisting

23:09.513 --> 23:12.766
that you get a job.

23:13.642 --> 23:15.269
Now.

23:15.311 --> 23:19.106
(SIGHS) Dad doesn't get me,

23:15.311 --> 23:19.106
but you do.

23:19.148 --> 23:21.942
That's why I love you.

23:19.148 --> 23:21.942
You're always there

23:19.148 --> 23:21.942
to protect me.

23:23.777 --> 23:26.613
But don't worry, Mom,

23:23.777 --> 23:26.613
I have a meeting

23:23.777 --> 23:26.613
later on today.

23:26.655 --> 23:28.324
You have a meeting for a job?

23:28.366 --> 23:29.742
Why didn't you tell me?

23:29.783 --> 23:31.535
Where? With whom?

23:29.783 --> 23:31.535
Can I help?

23:31.577 --> 23:33.037
I don't wanna jinx it.

23:33.079 --> 23:35.122
Say no more

23:33.079 --> 23:35.122
and I will ask no more.

23:36.290 --> 23:38.334
Oh, and I used your car

23:36.290 --> 23:38.334
and it's on empty.

23:38.376 --> 23:39.752
Do you want me

23:38.376 --> 23:39.752
to fill it up for you?

23:39.793 --> 23:42.963
What a sweet

23:39.793 --> 23:42.963
and thoughtful gesture.

23:43.005 --> 23:44.173
Should I put it

23:43.005 --> 23:44.173
on your credit card?

23:46.217 --> 23:47.801
Oh. (CHUCKLES)

23:49.345 --> 23:50.428
(CLEARS THROAT)

23:51.389 --> 23:53.140
Thanks, Mom. (KISSES)

23:56.602 --> 24:00.189
And so, when everything

23:56.602 --> 24:00.189
gets back into the lab,

23:56.602 --> 24:00.189
Eve'll give you a call, okay?

24:00.231 --> 24:01.439
It'll be fine.

24:04.360 --> 24:06.362
Sharon is trying to

24:04.360 --> 24:06.362
schedule a bunch of tests.

24:06.404 --> 24:07.780
She's on her way

24:06.404 --> 24:07.780
back from the farm.

24:07.821 --> 24:10.157
(SIGHS) I'll call her back.

24:10.199 --> 24:11.867
She's becoming a real pest.

24:13.911 --> 24:15.037
-What?

24:13.911 --> 24:15.037
-Sorry.

24:15.621 --> 24:16.997
No, it's okay.

24:19.250 --> 24:22.586
It's great, actually.

24:19.250 --> 24:22.586
Call Sharon back.

24:22.628 --> 24:24.213
Get the number for that farm

24:22.628 --> 24:24.213
where she boards her horse

24:24.255 --> 24:26.966
and get them on the phone

24:24.255 --> 24:26.966
for me, please.

24:24.255 --> 24:26.966
As soon as you can.

24:30.094 --> 24:31.469
Ben broke up with me.

24:31.511 --> 24:33.389
He's being totally

24:31.511 --> 24:33.389
unreasonable.

24:33.764 --> 24:34.681
(SCOFFS)

24:35.349 --> 24:36.600
It's broken.

24:36.642 --> 24:38.894
Hello, we're talking here.

24:38.936 --> 24:43.023
As I was saying, Ben is being

24:38.936 --> 24:43.023
completely unreasonable.

24:43.065 --> 24:44.400
When it comes

24:43.065 --> 24:44.400
to relationships,

24:44.442 --> 24:47.320
it's important to find someone

24:44.442 --> 24:47.320
who loves you for who you are,

24:47.361 --> 24:51.115
but you have to love them

24:47.361 --> 24:51.115
for who they are too

24:47.361 --> 24:51.115
and you have to admit,

24:51.157 --> 24:54.410
you haven't been

24:51.157 --> 24:54.410
as enthusiastic as Ben has

24:51.157 --> 24:54.410
about the two of you dating.

24:54.452 --> 24:55.493
That's true.

24:56.078 --> 24:57.537
No one asked you.

24:57.579 --> 24:58.956
Okay, but it's still true.

25:00.582 --> 25:02.542
You know what I think?

25:02.584 --> 25:04.502
I think that maybe

25:02.584 --> 25:04.502
all this is for the best.

25:05.503 --> 25:06.504
Ben and I don't

25:05.503 --> 25:06.504
belong together.

25:07.840 --> 25:09.758
Maybe we shouldn't

25:07.840 --> 25:09.758
even have started dating.

25:09.800 --> 25:12.219
If you really believed that,

25:09.800 --> 25:12.219
you wouldn't be here.

25:13.053 --> 25:14.847
No. (SIGHS)

25:14.888 --> 25:16.265
I really think it's over.

25:21.270 --> 25:22.855
It's not working.

25:22.896 --> 25:25.691
It's not broken.

25:22.896 --> 25:25.691
You're just not

25:22.896 --> 25:25.691
using it properly.

25:25.732 --> 25:28.735
Your intention was

25:25.732 --> 25:28.735
to only serve yourself.

25:28.777 --> 25:30.612
But I won't be

25:28.777 --> 25:30.612
serving anybody,

25:30.654 --> 25:33.699
because there's no way

25:30.654 --> 25:33.699
I can finish

25:30.654 --> 25:33.699
the centerpieces on time

25:33.740 --> 25:35.409
and Martha's going to take

25:33.740 --> 25:35.409
my business tonight

25:35.451 --> 25:37.077
when her dinner

25:35.451 --> 25:37.077
is flower free.

25:37.119 --> 25:37.870
So, you're giving up?

25:39.372 --> 25:42.082
I can't do it.

25:39.372 --> 25:42.082
Not by myself.

25:42.124 --> 25:45.794
Wouldn't it be better

25:42.124 --> 25:45.794
to try and fail

25:42.124 --> 25:45.794
than to just fail?

25:45.836 --> 25:48.130
No, what's the point

25:45.836 --> 25:48.130
of putting in the effort

25:48.172 --> 25:50.216
if you know there's

25:48.172 --> 25:50.216
no hope of succeeding?

25:50.257 --> 25:52.092
-(DOOR CHIMES)

25:50.257 --> 25:52.092
-There's always hope.

25:53.427 --> 25:55.553
-Hey.

25:53.427 --> 25:55.553
-Hi.

25:55.888 --> 25:57.181
Hi, Sam.

25:57.848 --> 25:59.557
Abigail.

25:59.599 --> 26:01.810
-I need to ask you a favor.

25:59.599 --> 26:01.810
-Name it.

26:01.852 --> 26:03.937
May I take Grace to

26:01.852 --> 26:03.937
the hospital, later today?

26:03.979 --> 26:05.563
Hospital?

26:05.605 --> 26:09.276
Oh, you know that thing

26:05.605 --> 26:09.276
that I'm not supposed

26:05.605 --> 26:09.276
to know or talk about?

26:09.318 --> 26:10.403
Yeah?

26:10.444 --> 26:12.071
I got a plan.

26:12.112 --> 26:13.697
I think you're

26:12.112 --> 26:13.697
rubbing off on me.

26:13.739 --> 26:15.949
And taking her

26:13.739 --> 26:15.949
to the hospital will help?

26:15.991 --> 26:17.410
Should be just what

26:15.991 --> 26:17.410
the doctor ordered.

26:18.160 --> 26:19.537
Pun intended.

26:21.038 --> 26:21.830
Well, good luck.

26:23.249 --> 26:24.791
I got this.

26:24.833 --> 26:26.752
Now, I have to go

26:24.833 --> 26:26.752
see a man about a horse.

26:26.793 --> 26:27.836
Literally.

26:30.630 --> 26:33.591
I can't believe Sam

26:30.630 --> 26:33.591
is still on the market.

26:30.630 --> 26:33.591
He's such a catch.

26:39.181 --> 26:40.933
So, what should we order?

26:40.974 --> 26:42.768
(SIGHS)

26:40.974 --> 26:42.768
Well, when I thought

26:40.974 --> 26:42.768
I might be pregnant,

26:42.809 --> 26:46.564
I went online,

26:42.809 --> 26:46.564
and there was a long list

26:42.809 --> 26:46.564
of things you shouldn't eat.

26:46.604 --> 26:48.399
-Oh, now you can have

26:46.604 --> 26:48.399
whatever you want.

26:46.604 --> 26:48.399
-(CHUCKLES)

26:49.816 --> 26:52.570
-Oysters?

26:49.816 --> 26:52.570
-We can split a dozen.

26:52.610 --> 26:55.697
All right, but you order

26:52.610 --> 26:55.697
your own souffle.

26:52.610 --> 26:55.697
I'm not sharing.

26:55.739 --> 26:56.614
(BOTH LAUGHING)

26:59.034 --> 27:02.288
-I'm sorry.

26:59.034 --> 27:02.288
-For what?

27:02.329 --> 27:04.957
For being all over

27:02.329 --> 27:04.957
the place about

27:02.329 --> 27:04.957
wanting to start a family.

27:04.998 --> 27:08.544
Hey, you are the sweetest,

27:08.586 --> 27:11.464
kindest, most caring

27:08.586 --> 27:11.464
person I know.

27:11.505 --> 27:15.217
You're already a great person,

27:11.505 --> 27:15.217
so you're gonna make

27:11.505 --> 27:15.217
a great mom.

27:15.259 --> 27:16.385
Are you saying you're ready?

27:18.220 --> 27:19.721
What do you think

27:18.220 --> 27:19.721
about getting a puppy?

27:21.014 --> 27:22.391
A puppy?

27:30.774 --> 27:31.775
What happened

27:30.774 --> 27:31.775
to your room?

27:32.318 --> 27:33.986
(CHUCKLES)

27:34.027 --> 27:34.778
Mom fixed it.

27:35.571 --> 27:36.654
(SCOFFS) Was it broken?

27:38.198 --> 27:40.284
-Dad.

27:38.198 --> 27:40.284
-It's your room.

27:40.326 --> 27:43.454
Yeah, you always

27:40.326 --> 27:43.454
tell me it's a mess.

27:43.496 --> 27:45.456
And that I should

27:43.496 --> 27:45.456
move where my desk is.

27:45.498 --> 27:47.874
Well, I might think that,

27:45.498 --> 27:47.874
but it's your space.

27:48.875 --> 27:50.043
Mom is...

27:50.085 --> 27:51.753
I can see you're not happy.

27:52.670 --> 27:54.672
But I should be.

27:54.714 --> 27:57.675
We're all together

27:54.714 --> 27:57.675
and there's no fighting.

27:58.385 --> 27:59.386
But you're not.

28:00.720 --> 28:03.432
-I love Mom.

28:00.720 --> 28:03.432
-She loves you.

28:03.474 --> 28:07.894
She hasn't lived

28:03.474 --> 28:07.894
with me since I was a kid,

28:03.474 --> 28:07.894
not full time anyway.

28:10.022 --> 28:12.149
I can talk to your mom,

28:10.022 --> 28:12.149
if you want.

28:12.191 --> 28:12.983
LINDA: Talk to me?

28:14.318 --> 28:15.402
About what?

28:15.902 --> 28:18.071
Um.

28:18.113 --> 28:22.284
Mom, wouldn't you be

28:18.113 --> 28:22.284
happier in your own place

28:18.113 --> 28:22.284
or back in New York?

28:24.744 --> 28:26.664
Sam, did you

28:24.744 --> 28:26.664
put him up to this?

28:26.704 --> 28:28.541
No, no, no, no, no.

28:26.704 --> 28:28.541
This wasn't Dad.

28:30.750 --> 28:35.130
Nick, you don't know

28:30.750 --> 28:35.130
what you need. I do.

28:35.172 --> 28:37.466
I have your best

28:35.172 --> 28:37.466
interests at heart.

28:40.052 --> 28:41.428
(SIGHS) Nick.

28:45.224 --> 28:46.225
It's not okay.

28:48.602 --> 28:51.021
You're so determined

28:48.602 --> 28:51.021
to control him,

28:51.063 --> 28:52.231
that you're gonna

28:51.063 --> 28:52.231
lose him.

28:53.773 --> 28:54.983
You can make things

28:53.773 --> 28:54.983
easier for him.

28:57.194 --> 28:58.529
I just don't know if you will.

29:05.077 --> 29:07.996
So I needed to drop off some

29:05.077 --> 29:07.996
lab work and I just thought

29:05.077 --> 29:07.996
you might wanna come with me.

29:08.038 --> 29:11.124
Thank you.

29:08.038 --> 29:11.124
This place is great.

29:11.166 --> 29:14.670
-We do share an

29:11.166 --> 29:14.670
affinity for science.

29:11.166 --> 29:14.670
-We do.

29:14.712 --> 29:16.630
We don't get to see enough

29:14.712 --> 29:16.630
of you, Dr. Radford.

29:17.756 --> 29:19.174
He's a fan favorite

29:17.756 --> 29:19.174
around here.

29:19.216 --> 29:20.926
Thank you.

29:20.967 --> 29:22.844
The nurses really

29:20.967 --> 29:22.844
like you here.

29:22.886 --> 29:24.471
Oh, well, this place

29:22.886 --> 29:24.471
has a terrific staff.

29:25.222 --> 29:26.432
What is this?

29:26.473 --> 29:28.975
I decided to take on

29:26.473 --> 29:28.975
an intern or two

29:29.017 --> 29:30.894
from your high school

29:29.017 --> 29:30.894
at my office.

29:30.936 --> 29:33.272
And as soon as I get

29:30.936 --> 29:33.272
the principal to sign on,

29:30.936 --> 29:33.272
it's a go.

29:34.440 --> 29:35.649
For somebody

29:34.440 --> 29:35.649
interested in science,

29:35.691 --> 29:37.484
it would be a really good

29:35.691 --> 29:37.484
learning experience.

29:38.569 --> 29:40.529
-You know anybody?

29:38.569 --> 29:40.529
-Why me?

29:42.406 --> 29:46.952
Look, um, I see

29:42.406 --> 29:46.952
a lot of people at their

29:42.406 --> 29:46.952
very worst moments.

29:46.993 --> 29:50.122
Especially when I was

29:46.993 --> 29:50.122
running the ER in New York.

29:50.163 --> 29:53.626
Death and dying is part of

29:50.163 --> 29:53.626
what I deal with every day.

29:53.667 --> 29:56.503
But I've learned

29:53.667 --> 29:56.503
that one way

29:53.667 --> 29:56.503
to heal from loss

29:56.545 --> 29:58.756
is to give your heart

29:56.545 --> 29:58.756
something else to love.

29:58.797 --> 30:00.633
Not to replace

29:58.797 --> 30:00.633
what it is you lost,

30:00.674 --> 30:02.175
but just to make

30:00.674 --> 30:02.175
the emptiness

30:02.884 --> 30:04.844
less empty.

30:07.931 --> 30:10.142
I know you miss your dad.

30:10.183 --> 30:13.520
And I wish I had

30:10.183 --> 30:13.520
more to offer you

30:10.183 --> 30:13.520
than an internship.

30:15.897 --> 30:16.940
But what do you say?

30:19.818 --> 30:21.820
I say, I better schedule

30:19.818 --> 30:21.820
my driving test.

30:22.279 --> 30:24.030
You're ready.

30:24.072 --> 30:25.865
-I am, thanks to you.

30:24.072 --> 30:25.865
-(CHUCKLING)

30:32.247 --> 30:36.669
The question my heroine

30:32.247 --> 30:36.669
poses to herself is,

30:36.710 --> 30:40.839
"Can you have a once

30:36.710 --> 30:40.839
in a life time love

30:36.710 --> 30:40.839
twice in a lifetime?"

30:42.257 --> 30:43.509
Sorry I'm late.

30:43.550 --> 30:47.471
Oh, don't apologize,

30:43.550 --> 30:47.471
this has been

30:43.550 --> 30:47.471
a real treat for me.

30:47.513 --> 30:50.849
-I didn't recognize

30:47.513 --> 30:50.849
that passage.

30:47.513 --> 30:50.849
-It's from his upcoming book.

30:50.890 --> 30:53.268
It's something I started

30:50.890 --> 30:53.268
before my wife died.

30:53.310 --> 30:55.395
It's beautiful.

30:53.310 --> 30:55.395
You really should finish it.

31:04.404 --> 31:05.864
A gift is totally unnecessary.

31:07.157 --> 31:07.949
Open it.

31:11.244 --> 31:14.707
I acquired this notebook

31:11.244 --> 31:14.707
at an estate sale in England.

31:14.748 --> 31:19.670
The woman who sold it to me

31:14.748 --> 31:19.670
said that the owner was

31:14.748 --> 31:19.670
a famous English writer.

31:19.712 --> 31:23.215
Apparently, it was

31:19.712 --> 31:23.215
the only blank notebook

31:19.712 --> 31:23.215
in his library.

31:23.256 --> 31:25.925
She said he kept it

31:23.256 --> 31:25.925
to remind him of the

31:23.256 --> 31:25.925
darkest time in his life.

31:25.967 --> 31:27.886
A time he lost his voice.

31:30.180 --> 31:31.682
It's too much.

31:31.724 --> 31:34.351
I was just holding it,

31:31.724 --> 31:34.351
waiting for the right person.

31:34.393 --> 31:37.145
And that's me?

31:37.187 --> 31:40.649
This inspiration you have,

31:37.187 --> 31:40.649
it doesn't lie within

31:37.187 --> 31:40.649
anyone else.

31:41.525 --> 31:44.069
Not your lovely wife.

31:44.110 --> 31:46.822
It's in you, and only

31:44.110 --> 31:46.822
you have the power

31:44.110 --> 31:46.822
to unlock it.

31:49.658 --> 31:52.661
Your wife is

31:49.658 --> 31:52.661
always with you.

31:52.703 --> 31:55.080
You don't have to find her.

31:52.703 --> 31:55.080
She's always there,

31:52.703 --> 31:55.080
in your heart.

31:57.791 --> 32:00.919
If you give up writing,

31:57.791 --> 32:00.919
you'll have lost

31:57.791 --> 32:00.919
two things you love.

32:01.879 --> 32:04.172
And your fans need you.

32:04.214 --> 32:05.924
There's a shortage of

32:04.214 --> 32:05.924
love stories in the world.

32:08.510 --> 32:09.762
Well, then,

32:08.510 --> 32:09.762
I better keep writing.

32:11.930 --> 32:14.433
